    "Furthermore, the encoding performance for unseen words was significant up to -700 ms before word onset, which provides evidence for the engagement of IFG in context-based next-word prediction 40.",
    "The zero-shot mapping results were robust in each individual participant and the group level (Fig. 2B -left, blue lines).",
    "For GPT-2 embeddings, the zero-shot encoding performance was close to zero when we randomly matched the words in the test fold with mismatching contextual embeddings (Figs. 2A, B and S1, black lines).",
    "Furthermore, the predicted neural activity pattern (brain embedding) for each unseen word was selective to the IFG.",
    "We did not find a statistically significant correlation between brain embedding and contextual embedding in an adjacent control area, the precentral gyrus (Fig. 2C, blue lines)."
